---
title: Spiced Cauliflower Steak with a Protein Packed Salad
description: If you’ve never had a cauliflower ‘steak’ it’s exactly what it sounds like: cauliflower sliced lengthwise into steak-like portions, seasoned, and either grilled or roasted (we roast ours in this recipe) until tender on the inside and crispy on the outside. Quinoa is an excellent source of plant-based protein, making it the perfect base for the salad. Seeds and dried fruit add another layer of texture to the dish, whilst a fresh squeeze of lemon and a handful of chopped coriander and a Greek yoghurt dressing keep the dish fresh and light.
